{"title":"看望一个人——在韶山","authors":["曹宇翔"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":2,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"看望一个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——在韶山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹宇翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩问中国民间一句很古的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知您在这个山冲居住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云　青山　如梦如歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如您当年潇洒的谈吐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我故乡的纯朴乡亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今庄稼丰收　或操办喜事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还说托了您的福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当知您喜欢吃肥肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辣子青菜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几位亲人牺牲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿补丁衣服"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最近他们守着家中电视"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失声痛哭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是您的出生之地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么清新的空气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么好的山色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是您晚年梦中的归宿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一阵歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响自阳光下的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不让我低头想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹雨　饥饿　雪山　草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您和一个苦难民族走过的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建立一个属于人民的国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下五卷传世的大书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为谁而受苦　为谁而操劳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱您的人民早些年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"习惯用明亮辽阔的蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作您的名片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面　有您劳累一生的职务"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是您当年南下队伍里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个连长的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山东老家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我童年的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就想到这里看看啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民间传说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您早已化作中国山河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地五谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我从童年就想到这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种情感隔着岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻心铭骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云　青山　如梦如歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远地向我倾注啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向阳山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静的简陋的老屋"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}